  "notes": "If you stow the gun mid-quote, its voice lines can continue while other weapons are equipped, letting you hear weapon-swap dialogue. A reload-cancel trick can transfer the crit-stacking behavior to other guns, and repeating it can create multiple independent instances for extremely high crit bonuses. This clears when you quit the game. Subtitles may truncate some lines, and selling it while equipped can make its voice lines trigger for other weapons until you restart.",
